metadata.name: Liquid Variations #1
metadata.description:
This artwork is a piece from the "Liquid Variations" collection which explores the ephemerality of movement, the unique moment that vanishes before the eyes but survives through photography.

Bianca Victal | 2021  
JPG: 3808 × 5712 px  
300 dpi  
6,8 MB
